---
// Privacy Policy / Datenschutz
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy — n8n-desk</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">n8n-desk</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="legal">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Responsible Party</h2>
    <p>
      Industrial Code &amp; Magic UG (haftungsbeschrankt)<br />
      c/o Factory Works GmbH<br />
      Rheinsberger Strasse 76/77<br />
      10115 Berlin, Germany<br />
      E-Mail: <a href="mailto:mail@industrial-code-and-magic.com">mail@industrial-code-and-magic.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
    <h3>Waitlist Registration</h3>
    <p>
      When you join the waitlist, we collect your <strong>email address</strong>. This is used solely to notify you about n8n-desk availability and updates. We do not share your email with third parties.
    </p>

    <h3>Website Hosting</h3>
    <p>
      This website is hosted on infrastructure that may log standard server access data (IP address, browser type, timestamp). These logs are used for security and operational purposes only and are not linked to personal profiles.
    </p>

    <h2>3. n8n-desk Application</h2>
    <p>
      n8n-desk is a desktop application that runs locally on your machine. It connects directly to your own n8n instance(s). We do not receive, store, or process any data from your n8n-desk sessions, workflows, conversations, or files. All data stays on your device and your n8n instance.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Legal Basis</h2>
    <p>
      Processing of your email address for the waitlist is based on your consent (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR). You can withdraw consent at any time by contacting us at the email above or using the unsubscribe link in any email we send.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
      We retain your waitlist email until you unsubscribe or request deletion. Server logs are retained for a maximum of 30 days.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Under GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, delete, restrict processing, and port your personal data. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. To exercise your rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:mail@industrial-code-and-magic.com">mail@industrial-code-and-magic.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      This website does not use cookies or tracking technologies.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
    </p>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <span class="footer-logo">n8n-desk</span>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/imprint">Imprint</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <style>
    :root {
      --neutral-125: hsl(0, 0%, 96%);
      --neutral-250: hsl(0, 0%, 80%);
      --neutral-300: hsl(0, 0%, 68%);
      --neutral-600: hsl(0, 0%, 46%);
      --neutral-800: hsl(0, 0%, 24%);
      --neutral-900: hsl(0, 0%, 13%);
      --neutral-950: hsl(0, 0%, 9%);
      --orange-300:  hsl(7, 100%, 68%);
      --orange-400:  hsl(7, 100%, 60%);

      --page-bg:        var(--neutral-950);
      --section-alt-bg: var(--neutral-900);
      --text-heading:   var(--neutral-125);
      --text-body:      var(--neutral-250);
      --text-muted:     var(--neutral-300);
      --text-disabled:  var(--neutral-600);
      --accent:         var(--orange-300);
      --accent-hover:   var(--orange-400);
      --border-subtle:  rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      --max-width: 1120px;
      --transition: 150ms ease;
    }

    html { -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: var(--page-bg);
      color: var(--text-body);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { color: var(--accent-hover); }

    .nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(23, 23, 23, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--text-heading);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .legal {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 120px 24px 80px;
    }
    .legal h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-heading);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .legal .subtitle {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .legal h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-heading);
      margin: 32px 0 12px;
    }
    .legal h3 {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-heading);
      margin: 20px 0 8px;
    }
    .legal p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .footer {
      background: var(--section-alt-bg);
      padding: 40px 24px 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    }
    .footer-inner {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .footer-links a {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-disabled);
      transition: color var(--transition);
    }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  </style>

</body>
</html>
